646 in the third. A new teacher would receive $ 23,000 yearly, and an educator with 14 years of experience and a doctorate, who teaches summer school, could earn up to $ 64,000 under the proposed pay scale, he said. `` It's a nationally recognized idea that teachers should be paid more for the work they do,'' <PERSON> Gollan </PERSON> said.
